UNITED STATES ex rel. LAU CHIU, Appellant v. Rudolph REIMER, Commissioner of Immigration, Appellee. No. 103. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 25, 1940. Samuel B. Wasserman, of New York City, for appellant. J. Randall Creel, of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, CHASE, and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed on opinion below. 36 F.Supp. 523.
